<li>[1] International Agency for Research on Cancer (IARC). 2023. “<a href="https://www.iarc.who.int/reference/expanding-global-access-to-radiotherapy/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Expanding Global Access to Radiotherapy.</a>”</li>



<li>[2] American Society for Radiation Oncology (ASTRO). 2020. “<a href="https://www.astro.org/ASTRO/media/ASTRO/News%20and%20Publications/Press%20Kits/PDFs/2020/AM20_PressSlidesMaroongroge203.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Geographic Access to Radiation Therapy in the United States.</a>” ASTRO Press Kit.</li>



